-= Kitchen =-
This is going to sound unbelievable, but you've just entered a kitchen. Let's see what's in here.

Oh, great. Here's a fridge. Now why would someone leave that there? The fridge contains a raw pork chop. You see an oven. Suddenly, you bump your head on the ceiling, but it's not such a bad bump that it's going to prevent you from looking at objects and even things. You make out a table. You shudder, but continue examining the table. On the table you make out a cookbook. Look over there! a counter. You see a red hot pepper and a knife on the counter. Oh wow!
